{"tid":2278731,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【操守監管】瑞信錯誤報價 證監罰款210萬","createTime":"2020-11-09T10:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T10:28:38.000Z","uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"36a51b9aac0f695cf51f0530895abe88741ab225","tid":2278731,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:25:06.000Z","msg":"雞到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n證監會指，瑞士信貸證券(香港)因違反電子交易規定，遭譴責及罰款210萬元。<br />\n證監會發現，瑞信在2019年2月28日上午9時39分至9時47分期間，向市場發送16,935項錯誤莊家報價，導致以偏離當時市價的價格執行了8,042項股票期權買賣。該事故源於作為股票期權莊家的瑞信，在產生莊家報價時所使用的符號配對程式出現邏輯錯誤所致。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edigest.hk/article/202601/投資/操守監管瑞信錯誤報價-證監罰款210萬/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2Farticle%2F202601%2F%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%2F%E6%93%8D%E5%AE%88%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1%E7%91%9E%E4%BF%A1%E9%8C%AF%E8%AA%A4%E5%A0%B1%E5%83%B9-%E8%AD%89%E7%9B%A3%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE210%E8%90%AC%2F&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=59161891\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edigest.hk/article/202601/投資/操守監管瑞信錯誤報價-證監罰款210萬/</a>"},{"pid":"390d3e28e20e6f04b9bc52713465c059cb0ae8b5","tid":2278731,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:27:03.000Z","msg":"雖然唔知佢開錯價係益左邊一邊<br />\n但不嬲都唔會玩兩瑞嘅instrument"},{"pid":"06a4b81c8eb9506f99cc9f409607afb75d7f57da","tid":2278731,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"390d3e28e20e6f04b9bc52713465c059cb0ae8b5","tid":2278731,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:27:03.000Z","msg":"雖然唔知佢開錯價係益左邊一邊<br />\n但不嬲都唔會玩兩瑞嘅instrument"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:28:38.000Z","msg":"4大閪商<br />\n<br />\n匯海兩瑞🚬"}]}